1.自我介绍
我从事了5年以上的后端设计和开发工作,既有从0到1构建项目的经验,也有重构和优化复杂系统的经验,我之前的业务经验主要集中在电商风控领域,虽然和该岗位的业务相关性较弱,但是我的学习能力比较强,并且善于将工程技术融入到不同业务场景去推动业务发展,比如我曾在跨业务背景下主导重构过一个qps在3000左右的电商风控服务,重构后服务的延迟和吞吐量都有30%以上的提升,从而间接提高了业务的可靠性,而且在平时工作时我也特别关注项目的开发质量以及项目上线后的运行质量,并且注重把一些关键流程和解决方案整理成细节文档方便后续追踪,我觉得我的这些经历还是能够让我应对该岗位的一些挑战的


I’ve been working as a backend developer for over 5 years. My experience covers everything from building projects from scratch to optimizing complex legacy systems.
Although my background is mainly in e-commerce risk control, I’m a quick learner and good at applying technical skills to new business scenarios. A good example is when I led a major refactoring project for a risk service handling about 3,000 QPS. After the optimization, we saw a 30% boost in performance and throughput, which really helped the business stability.
I also care a lot about development quality and documentation to ensure long-term maintainability. I believe these experiences make me a strong candidate for this position.






背景:
我所在的风控部门有多个团队,我所属团队主要负责维护一个风控数据处理平台,我们的主要目标是给它接入更多的业务场景数据来提高这个平台在部门内的普及率,我们的兄弟团队负责维护一个数据驱动的电商风控服务,随着业务体量的变大,这个服务的维护成本和可靠性都在变差,靠简单的增量修复已经无法解决问题,所以如果能把这个服务彻底重构并接入到我们团队内部的数据处理平台上的话,既能给我们的平台增加新的业务场景,也能借重构解决旧服务的一系列问题

The risk control department I work in consists of multiple teams. The team I belong to is primarily responsible for maintaining a risk control data processing platform. Our main objective is to integrate more business scenario data into this platform in order to increase its adoption rate within the department.
Our sibling team is responsible for maintaining a legacy e-commerce risk control service. As the business volume has grown, the maintenance cost and reliability of this service have been deteriorating. Simple incremental fixes are no longer sufficient to resolve the underlying issues.
Therefore, if we could completely refactor this service and integrate it into our internal data processing platform, it would serve a dual purpose: it would add new business scenarios to our platform, and the refactoring would address the series of problems of the legacy service.


2.最成功的项目
a.在跨团队背景下重构了一个核心电商风控服务,提升了业务可靠性和自身业务平台的普及率,积累了跨团队协作的经验
b.通过和算法团队合作实现落地了一项适用于当前广告业务的机器学习算法,显著提升了广告业务的投放准确率

Refactored a core e-commerce risk control service in a cross-team context, enhancing both business reliability and the adoption rate of our internal platform while gaining valuable experience in cross-team collaboration.

Collaborated with the algorithm team to implement a dedicated machine learning tecnical for the advertising business at that time, significantly improving the targeting accuracy of ad delivery.


3.担任什么角色
我在这个项目里担任主架构和协调员的角色
I served as the lead architect and coordinator on this project.


4.最大的挑战
这个项目最大的挑战包含业务和技术两方面

The biggest challenges of this project fell into two categories: business and technical.

首先在业务方面有两个挑战:
我们需要在跨团队背景下重构一个会影响核心业务的服务,让双方团队达成高效共识并且分工协作完成这次重构是一大挑战
因为待重构的服务是对方团队维护的,我们团队并不熟悉它的业务逻辑和技术实现

First, on the business side, there were two main challenges:
We needed to refactor a service critical to core business operations within a cross-team context. Getting both teams to reach an efficient consensus and coordinate their efforts to complete this refactoring was a major challenge.
Furthermore, since the service being refactored was maintained by the other team, our team was not familiar with its business logic or technical implementation.

另外在技术方面也有两个挑战:
重构之后怎么保证在不影响业务的前提下实现旧服务到新服务的平滑迁移
我们设定了一系列量化指标来判断重构后的效果,比如重构后服务可靠性,延迟,吞吐量,可维护性必须提升多少个百分点,能否达到这些指标也是一大挑战



In addition, on the technical side, there were also two challenges:
How to ensure a seamless migration from the old service to the new one without impacting ongoing business operations after the refactoring.
We established a series of quantitative metrics to evaluate the refactoring. For instance, we set specific percentage improvement targets for post-refactoring service reliability, latency, throughput, and maintainability. Meeting these targets was another significant challenge.




5.怎么解决挑战

和对方团队保持深入讨论和沟通,用现状数据证明这次重构的必要性,在对方的协助下深入了解待重构项目的所有业务和技术细节,制定明确的分工计划、分阶段目标和进度时间表,并且把重构过程出现的关键问题和阶段成果都落地成文档方便追溯

